Hi people. I have updated to 1.5.1 and have downloaded some stock planes.

What I am finding is that the elevons are not working. Even if I take them off, save craft and then put new ones on.

Is this something others are seeing or do I have  setting wrong somewhere?
Some pics would help.  And where did you download them from?  Include some of the craft files you downloaded so we can take a look.

Will upload the .craft file.
